parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission control module can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to issues with shifting into park, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The "Shift to Park" message is displayed
the vehicle fails to shut off
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
the parking gear needs to be repaired.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping and stalling can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission flares going into and out of second gear
the vehicle feels as if it's about to stall

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver assist system can cause the vehicle's AC and thermostat to malfunction, leading to discomfort and potential safety issues.
symptoms: The error code for driver assist is reduced
and the thermostat is locked at cold.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to register the vehicle as being in park can cause the engine to remain running, preventing the driver from turning off the vehicle, and potentially leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The dash displays an error message "Shift to Park" when the vehicle is already in park
the vehicle will not turn off
and the vehicle may not start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning door locks can cause safety issues, such as being locked out of the vehicle or unable to exit the vehicle in an emergency.
symptoms: The doors do not lock or unlock with the key fob
the buttons on the door to lock/unlock do not work
and the doors may lock or unlock randomly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The touch display screen constantly goes through every setting on the car while driving
and makes phone calls if a phone is detected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning steering assist can cause loss of control of the vehicle, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: and the vehicle may display a "Drive with Care" notification.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The battery issues can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, potentially leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: and the vehicle may not start or stall intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning rear hood can cause safety issues, such as the hood closing unexpectedly or not closing properly.
symptoms: The rear hood does not close or open properly
and the rear hood struts may leak fluid.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to recognize the vehicle is in park can cause the vehicle to remain in gear, making it difficult or impossible to turn off the engine, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle displays a "Shift to Park" message
even when the vehicle is already in park; the vehicle will not turn off; the radio and other accessories remain on; the vehicle may not lock doors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The infotainment system changes screens without being touched; the system displays the backup camera while driving forward; the system fails to display GPS directions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: causing the vehicle to shut off while driving; the vehicle's steering and brakes malfunction; the vehicle's battery drains quickly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to shift to park can cause the vehicle to remain running, leading to battery drain, overheating, and potential accidents.
The failure of the steering assist system can cause loss of power steering, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: engine fan coming on full blast

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the coolant temperature probe can cause the engine to overheat, leading to potential engine damage and accidents.
symptoms: engine fan coming on full blast.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to potential accidents and inconvenience.
